{"tid":1311134,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"歡迎光臨上水 麻煩入一入黎","createTime":"2019-07-13T04:50:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-13T05:43:26.000Z","uid":230422,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8415de8de5d68b31347f6eaa642108593a389ead","tid":1311134,"uid":230422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T04:50:18.000Z","msg":"好多謝咁多位去上水一日遊既朋友！<br />\n<br />\n要講到上水 除左著名既水貨街<br />\n唔好唔記得仲有大名鼎鼎既 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">上水廣場</span></span>!<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n上水廣場受盡同胞愛戴<br />\n入面應有盡有<br />\n大家行上水行到又熱又攰<br />\n推介你地入一入上水廣場嘆下冷氣之餘<br />\n又可以行下上水廣場 一齊行街街<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n上水廣場交通方便<br />\n專為大家而設<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bxhV7R4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbxhV7R4.png&h=cc3ef80c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cd7944f6a5bcc1a6c339b6f1d749e5b071f3a32e","tid":1311134,"uid":6294,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T04:50:35.000Z","msg":"我今日光復上水，<br />\n聽日去沙田野餐。<br />\n沙田死線，7月21日金鐘升級。<br />\n<br />\n兄弟爬山，各有各做<br />\n不割蓆，不分裂"},{"pid":"c716686f26ea9f690768319c06cf48c8eeae952c","tid":1311134,"uid":230422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T04:51:58.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04ede0b8becb3d2306e9400dfefdfdf50fa84af1","tid":1311134,"uid":230422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T04:53:55.000Z","msg":"再自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60549ec4aec84bce0e859e8f598251726d7ee210","tid":1311134,"uid":23042